{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Super Senseless Soccer is a football game where your goal is not just to score goals: instead, you create powerful synergies and combos in order to collect ridiculous amounts of money!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>It's SUPER! It's SENSELESS! It's SOCCER!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328320/extras/steam-banner-1.png?t=1730863899\" /><strong></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Every game starts out as a standard 5-a-side football match, but you very quickly learn that the rules are meant to be broken in increasingly hilarious ways:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Equip your players with weapons</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Add a Sheep, Goose, Dog or Cat</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Recruit a variety of Special Team Mates (including the Referee)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Hurl random objects at your opponents</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Jump onto the field as a Manager... and more!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328320/extras/steam-banner-2.png?t=1730863899\" /></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">With more than a hundred different upgrades available, every game is guaranteed to be unique and different. </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Mix different Upgrade Tickets, Player Traits and Special Team Mates to unlock game breaking combos!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">How about multiple balls on the field at once? Easily done! </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A completely lopsided 11 vs 5 match? Perfectly normal! </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Millions of dollars from a single combo? You got it!!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"b